<div class="container">
  <div class="jumbotron designstages">
    <%= image_tag 'DesignProcessIcon.png',
      alt: 'the design proccess', class: 'processhead' %>
  </div>

  <div class="row marketing">
    <div class="col-lg-12 ">
      <div class="col-lg-6 hidden-xs">
        <%= image_tag 'NapkinIcon.png', class: 'designPhoto',
          alt: 'Idea Written on a Cocktail Napkin' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 explanation">
        <h4>Develop</h4>
        <p>You have a great idea and need to get it started. Choose this option if you need design assistance. You can get feedback on the feasibility of your idea and what is needed to develop.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-12 ">
      <div class="col-lg-6 hidden-xs">
        <a href="http://mmatch.herokuapp.com/spaces">
          <%= image_tag 'BlueprintIcon.png', class:'designPhoto', alt:'design blueprints' %>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 explanation">
        <h4>Prototype</h4>
        <p>You’ve made detailed specifications.  All of your supplies are listed and you’re pretty sure what tools are needed to build it. Click here if you just need to find someone with the tools and drive to bring your idea into reality. Let's test it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-12 ">
      <div class="col-lg-6 hidden-xs">
        <%= image_tag 'BatchProduction.png', class: 'designPhoto', alt: 'Batch Production' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 explanation">
        <h4>Production</h4>
        <p>
          Maker Match can take your finished workable prototype, a blueprint or a 3D printer schematic
          and find a reliable maker that can manufacture your product in scalable batch orders.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
</div> <!-- /container -->

<%= render 'layouts/footer' %>


